,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T02:56:21.000Z","msg":"南昌新商場V Walk位於港鐵南昌站上蓋，交通便利，預計在2019年第三季開幕。商場佔地30萬平方呎，長達400米，<span style=\"color: red;\">面向海景</span>，匯集約150間商店，當中包括戲院、美食、美妝、潮流服飾。在早前，嘉禾院線已宣布進駐商場，大概開設5個影院，提供逾 400 個座位。美食方面，STARBUCKS、天仁茗茶、茶木、牛角燒肉專門店、峰壽司、原味家作等等人氣店鋪都已經確定開店。而最近，服裝品牌UNIQLO亦宣布進駐。<br />\n<br />\n咁多野行，淨係睇個海景都抵哂啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5768224fda8e9bd3374e666658b7e462642d56b1","tid":1325634,"uid":156936,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"9b20f0b71f784eb5b5757619498c9ad0852cd32c","tid":1325634,"uid":25833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cc35c4c77addc2e4c79154ae6504d1540f9e3640","tid":1325634,"uid":156936,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T02:52:55.000Z","msg":"個名改得咁好呀<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>V煞 Walk</strong></span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LcB4N7g.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLcB4N7g.jpg&h=d92d46cf&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T02:54:11.000Z","msg":"如果帶呢個面具行商場會點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T02:56:26.000Z","msg":"嚇撚死班業主同大陸旅客"},{"pid":"e9c28dace3a95b74dbb0dbfd2d6ec62994a3b7e8","tid":1325634,"uid":218813,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T03:03:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好開心又有新地商場可以去支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63ba5cc5f1a2d37533970512f98b7d0ab0c02876","tid":1325634,"uid":25833,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e9c28dace3a95b74dbb0dbfd2d6ec